1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:46,710 --> 00:00:47,550
(Jiang Ruoli,)

4
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:51,790
(why do you stir my heart?)

5
00:00:54,790 --> 00:00:55,630
Yanzhi,

6
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,600
everything I've done

7
00:01:01,350 --> 00:01:02,960
is truly for you.

8
00:01:17,590 --> 00:01:18,430
Jiang Ruoli.

9
00:01:44,350 --> 00:01:45,200
Watch out!

10
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:58,150
Yanzhi!

11
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,320
Yanzhi!

12
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,680
(Yuan.)

13
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,520
Yuan,

14
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,280
today is your birthday.

15
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:41,080
I swear here and now:

16
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,200
For all the remaining years,

17
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,000
I'll do everything

18
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,910
to keep you safe

19
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,710
and never abandon you.

20
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:50,590
(It's Yanzhi.)

21
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,800
(Has he remembered everything?)

22
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,840
Yanzhi.

23
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,200
Yuan,

24
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,280
happy birthday.

25
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:04,510
This SilverScales armor

26
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,750
is the heirloom token
of the Huo patriarch.

27
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:09,800
Would you accept it
as your birthday gift?

28
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,560
What's this?

29
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,626
This armor is called SilverScales.

30
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:23,590
It followed my ancestors

31
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,166
through hundreds of battles,

32
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,520
protecting its master.

33
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:28,150
It's a treasured heirloom

34
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,030
of the Huo clan.

35
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,400
Today,

36
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,870
I wish to give it to you.

37
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:40,296
This is the token of the Huo patriarch.

38
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:42,280
You don't deserve it.

39
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,400
Oh?

40
00:03:43,710 --> 00:03:44,800
You don't like it?

41
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,430
Yuan,

42
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,630
I know you still think

43
00:04:01,793 --> 00:04:04,193
about the dream you shared
with Huo Linchuan in a past life.

44
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,806
But whatever he could give you,

45
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,360
I can give you tenfold.

46
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,470
I can still give you

47
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:12,190
what he can't offer you.

48
00:04:16,702 --> 00:04:17,718
(Marriage Contract)
Look.

49
00:04:17,750 --> 00:04:19,070
Even if you despise me,

50
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,080
I've won

51
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,510
this game.

52
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,520
You and I

53
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,040
shall share the same bed in life

54
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,190
and the same resting place in death.

55
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,000
Humph.

56
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:33,110
Lu Huaijin,

57
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,160
go to your doom!

58
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,320
Yuan,

59
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:47,160
I'll let this strike

60
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,240
vent your anger.

61
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,520
You try to kill me,

62
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:53,920
but it's all in vain.

63
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,760
For I am

64
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,190
destined by heaven.

65
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,560
How could someone like Huo Linchuan,

66
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,310
a mere mortal, stand against me?

67
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:07,790
Yuan,

68
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,800
don't be afraid.

69
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,950
I won't hurt you.

70
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,870
In our last life,

71
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,600
when I took you hostage on that cliff,

72
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,920
it became my greatest regret.

73
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,680
I never meant to harm you.

74
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,680
Please, believe me.

75
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:25,560
Is that so?

76
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:28,043
Yet you drove my parents
to their deaths.

77
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:30,120
Is that what you call

78
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:31,270
love?

79
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:32,800
In this life,

80
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,070
I never wanted

81
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,360
to take your parents' lives.

82
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,720
I only meant

83
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:41,560
to use Jiang Huaikang

84
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:45,360
to sever your bond with Huo Linchuan.

85
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:49,630
But Huo Linchuan dared to harm you.

86
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:52,390
Still, it doesn't matter.

87
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:54,630
Anyone who ever laid a hand on you

88
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:56,360
must pay with their life.

89
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:00,680
You've tormented Huo Linchuan

90
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,920
through ten reincarnations.

91
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:05,120
You think that means victory.

92
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,190
But in my eyes,

93
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:10,510
you're just a coward who twists fate

94
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:12,750
and refuses to face your own heart.

95
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:13,590
No.

96
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:15,230
That's not true.

97
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,840
Let her go!

98
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:25,910
Yuan.

99
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:27,230
Yanzhi.

100
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,000
It's all my fault.

101
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:30,750
I couldn't recognize you sooner.

102
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:32,070
Huo Linchuan,

103
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,070
you finally remember

104
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,335
the taste of being dragged

105
00:06:35,346 --> 00:06:37,240
into despair by me.

106
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:40,800
Again and again,

107
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,680
in the end,

108
00:06:42,270 --> 00:06:44,680
you'll still fall by my hand.

109
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:47,230
Huo Linchuan!

110
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,310
Die!

111
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,000
Draw your blade!

112
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,510
Why won't you?

113
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,600
Kill me!

114
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,440
Lu Huaijin,

115
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,390
this is the 11th time.

116
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,950
Why still cling to this delusion?

117
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,480
How false.

118
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:14,710
Huaijin,

119
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:16,800
if you stop now,

120
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,390
we can still be as close as kin.

121
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:21,150
Shut your mouth.

122
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,270
You're just like Huo Wenyuan.

123
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,360
Sweet words, venomous heart.

124
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,070
Utterly deceitful.

125
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,360
Who do you truly despise?

126
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:32,510
Me, or the self trapped in time's cycle?

127
00:07:32,870 --> 00:07:35,070
Let the Huo clan perish!

128
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,320
Lu Huaijin,

129
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,840
stop.

130
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,830
You're not of Duke Huo's blood.

131
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,120
Nonsense!

132
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,400
Yuan,

133
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:55,750
to save him,

134
00:07:57,510 --> 00:07:58,680
you dared to deceive me?

135
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,750
My mother's keepsake still exists.

136
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,950
Huo Wenyuan took me in.

137
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,640
Tell me.

138
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:08,120
Were all my years of humiliation

139
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:10,360
nothing but a lie?

140
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,200
Lu Huaijin,

141
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,160
don't make the same mistake again.

142
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,150
Tell me.

143
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,070
Tell me why.

144
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,840
Yuan,

145
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,560
why couldn't you

146
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,800
love me once,

147
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,720
even if just for a moment?

148
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,480
You've been blinded by hollow hatred,

149
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:30,950
dragging everyone
into endless cycles of pain.

150
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:34,000
You brought all of this

151
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,510
upon yourself.

152
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,350
No.

153
00:08:37,670 --> 00:08:38,720
It's not true.

154
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,000
It's not true!

155
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,200
You lied to me!

156
00:08:41,910 --> 00:08:42,960
Impossible!

157
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:44,390
Huaijin,

158
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,480
stop this now.

159
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:49,550
Huo Linchuan,

160
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,720
you've been working together!

161
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,790
You must die today!

162
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,160
Yunzhou.

163
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:56,990
Yunzhou!

164
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:23,390
♪The dream shattered♪

165
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:25,430
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

166
00:09:25,430 --> 00:09:27,070
♪Like a restless soul♪

167
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:29,510
♪How vague♪

168
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:31,430
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

169
00:09:31,430 --> 00:09:33,670
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

170
00:09:34,470 --> 00:09:37,070
♪Love and hate entwined♪

171
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:40,390
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

172
00:09:41,030 --> 00:09:45,790
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

173
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:47,910
♪When fate falls apart♪

174
00:09:48,310 --> 00:09:51,870
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

175
00:09:52,590 --> 00:09:54,150
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

176
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:58,270
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

177
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:01,830
♪Life after life♪

178
00:10:02,310 --> 00:10:04,990
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

179
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:09,710
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

180
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:12,830
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

181
00:10:12,990 --> 00:10:14,390
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

182
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:17,510
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

183
00:10:17,590 --> 00:10:19,030
♪Now shatter apart♪

184
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:22,910
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

185
00:10:23,630 --> 00:10:26,430
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

186
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:29,550
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

187
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:34,270
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

188
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:37,430
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

189
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:41,990
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

190
00:10:42,190 --> 00:10:47,910
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

191
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:51,070
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

192
00:10:51,310 --> 00:10:54,030
♪Sober or indulge♪

193
00:10:54,470 --> 00:11:00,470
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
